      "type": "ApplicabilityConstraint",
      "name": "Non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw — ASTM F1717 static loading domain",
      "description": "Applicability is restricted to solid (non-cannulated) pedicle screws with nominal outer diameter 7.0–8.0 mm, rod diameter 5.5 mm, and construct geometry conforming to ASTM F1717 Section 6 (two-vertebra surrogate blocks, 35 mm inter-body spacing). Loading is limited to quasi-static axial compression-bending at a single prescribed displacement rate (5 mm/min). Dynamic, fatigue, and torsional loading modes are explicitly out of scope. Material properties must fall within the Ti-6Al-4V ELI property envelope (E = 113 ± 5 GPa, σ_y = 880 ± 30 MPa) characterised in the supporting coupon test dataset."
    },
    "hasOperatingEnvelope": {
