      "name": "F1717 compression-bending operating envelope — geometric and loading bounds",
      "description": "Operating envelope bounds: screw outer diameter 7.0–8.0 mm; screw length 40–55 mm; rod diameter 5.5 mm ± 0.05 mm; inter-body spacing 35 mm ± 1 mm; applied displacement 0–50 mm at 5 mm/min ± 0.5 mm/min; ambient temperature 20–25 °C; relative humidity 30–60% RH. FEA mesh density: minimum 4 elements through cortical shell thickness (≥ 0.3 mm element size); contact penalty stiffness 1×10⁵ N/mm. Extrapolation beyond these bounds requires re-validation."
