        "description": "All test conditions must be documented and controlled per ASTM F1717 Section 7 (displacement rate 5 mm/min, ambient temperature 20–25°C, dry conditions). Environmental monitoring records must be available for all test sessions. The limitation of a single test condition (one loading rate, one temperature) must be explicitly acknowledged and its impact on QoI uncertainty assessed. Multi-condition testing is not required at this MRL but would increase confidence."
