      "rationale": "Test conditions fully documented per ASTM F1717: displacement rate 5.0 ± 0.1 mm/min (verified by load frame calibration certificate), ambient temperature 22 ± 1°C (continuous thermocouple monitoring), dry conditions (no simulated body fluid). Environmental monitoring records available for all test sessions. Limitation acknowledged: single loading rate tested; rate-sensitivity of Ti-6Al-4V at quasi-static rates is negligible (<0.5% QoI variation per published literature), and the ASTM F1717 standard prescribes a single rate. Gradation 3 achieved: conditions documented and controlled; single-condition limitation acknowledged with impact assessment. This factor achieves exactly the required level; no shortfall."
